[It is most helpful to have these complete laboratory results and
some recent epidemiological information. We look forward to similar
reports in the near future, as there is much to be learned from this
outbreak. - Mod.PC]
[In the report, the number of susceptible animals is identical to the number
of destroyed animals. Dead animals should not be counted within the
destroyed animals. - Mod.AS]
